<h1>Termination Competitions

<p>The 
  <a href="http://termination-portal.org/wiki/Termination_Competition">
     International Termination Competitions
  are run on 
  <a href="http://www.starexec.org">
     Star-Exec.

<p>We provide here these extra features:
  <ul>
    <li>
      computation and display of results per category
    <li>
      flexible 2-dimensional results tables (x-axis: solver, y-axis: benchmark) (with filters for rows and columns, sorters, etc.)
    <li>
      caching (and permanent storage) of results (we intend to include also results of earlier competitions)


